            <title>[DERBY-4203] Change mailjdbc and sstest system tests to be able to restart with the existing database instead of creating a new one so they can be used for upgrade testing</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-4203</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It would be nice to have the system tests be able to pick up with an existing database instead of creating a new one, so they can be used for soft upgrade and hard upgrade testing after running a while with the old version.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
